Parsing phase
There must be a difference between the client route and the criteria route since the client route must contain some queues of departures and inversions. I have to do some process in order to have the clients to depart grouped by destination route.

First PSO
I have a correct pso for the rarb criteria. But it is too slow. I have to optimize the distance computation.
PSO with 'rarb' criteria but without pass thru.

PSO with rarb criteria done!!!
I added the apply function and now we can pass through a solution when we are really fast.
Prototype done. There is a problem resolving the inversions. This cause the distance to be longer than it should be. Gonna branch to try some modifications
